{"tid":1599037,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］唔該咁多個理性連登仔入哂黎 唔係要證據就係狗/五毛","createTime":"2019-09-27T18:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T18:24:05.000Z","uid":2932,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"304beba7fb1607f6eb30b1d1333a5f20982e7577","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">對唔住請留意同細心聽一聽</span></span><br />\n如果真係要大眾關注，相信性暴力事件，係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">必須</span></span>要有受害者企出嚟指證。<br />\n<br />\n喺世界各地，無論任何多恐怖嘅性暴力事件，性侵事件，獸父強姦女兒十多年，輪姦等等等等，都需要當事人企出嚟指證，無論事件有多恐怖，受害人有多崩潰，都必須要企出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">我哋絕對唔可以</span></span>因為受害人已經崩潰啦，就唔使佢哋企出嚟指證，我哋自己喺度聽傳言就相信，咁樣同藍絲廢佬係冇分別嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我哋而家最困難嘅係</span></span>受害人沒有警方保護，反而會受警方恐嚇，所以冇辦法可以公正同埋安全咁樣企出嚟指證警方。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">解決辦法</span></span><br />\n受害人或者知情人，被通知消息人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">必須</span></span>尋求外國官員，以及外國人權組織協助將事件證實為真實，不透過香港渠道調查，或將受害人送外國檢查以及政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">事件必須從國際以及聯合國方式制裁香港警察，不要再在香港以訛傳訛</span></span>"},{"pid":"2383333df8ccd155f22cfcba72acc1d418d2cde4","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4f0202758d77cb07cdbd1cb21cc5dc0595b1d79","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:06:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"262d5e9cac6db373d138762454f8962802f0e9c2","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de6a93ee5b3c768239bbf5bd98c45eb08cb7d980","tid":1599037,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:08:36.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n繼續作埋啲provocative嘅故仔對成個movement冇任何幫助"},{"pid":"984b18eb190aa59415dd9c063931f6f0321457aa","tid":1599037,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:08:46.000Z","msg":"另外大家記住<br />\n呢件事如果核爆<br />\n香港係一定進入內戰"},{"pid":"dd6c1b095bbc4a6cdf025104fcd716ffb3aa7d6a","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:10:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"b8a8e9241ecd546ace2b37e7e483a7e68d6a87db","tid":1599037,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:11:44.000Z","msg":"推推先 <br />\n但我地會保護受害手足 <br />\n金錢 人生安全保護 我地都可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906c101a623ca50be12dfbb6133783d9c94311ec","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e9d0ccfbfaeffa31295160a4e9884c80c5743e2","tid":1599037,"uid":2932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}